{"id":11,"date":"2020-04-24T09:23:43","date_gmt":"2020-04-24T08:23:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hale.uk\/?page_id=11"},"modified":"2023-10-04T12:33:12","modified_gmt":"2023-10-04T11:33:12","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/hale.uk\/about","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<section class=\"about\" data-colour=\"light\">\n\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t<h1>About<\/h1>\n\t\t\t<section>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p1\">Ambitious plans demand an experienced team that is dedicated to realising your vision. We are specialists in complex, high-quality construction projects, offering service and results that meet the expectations of the most discerning clients. We work together with leading architects and designers, throughout London and the southern counties.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/hale-brochure-apr-2023-for-web.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"underline light\">Download our brochure<\/a><\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t<h1>How We Work<\/h1>\n\t\t\t<section>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p1\">The quality of our finished projects is testament to our focus on each element of the building process. From cost management and procurement, through to programming, site management and the robust construction details we employ for maximum longevity, a culture of care runs through all we do.<\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Meticulous organisation and proactive communication are central to the way we work, as are the latest technology and software, which we integrate throughout our operations.<\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">We know it\u2019s about more than the results \u2013 the journey has to be right als<span class=\"s1\">o. For us, ev<\/span>ery project is a collaboration with you and your design team, who share our goal of delivering an exemplary finished building. We make personal service a priority throughout, from day one through to final delivery and beyond.<\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Our years of working this way are reflected in the long-standing relationships we enjoy with both clients and architects today.<\/p>\n\t\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t<h1>The Team<\/h1>\n\t\t\t<section>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p1\">We\u2019ve built a team and a select list of partners we can trust to deliver the success of your project, and our business. They&#8217;re people who take pride in every step \u2013 before, during and after the project.<\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">We are committed to the continuous development of our team. By identifying individual needs and investing in training, we make sure everyone adds to their skillset, and grows professionally as a leader in their field.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/about\/#anchor\/team\" target=\"_self\" class=\"underline light\">Meet the Team<\/a><\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t<h1>Accreditations<\/h1>\n\t\t\t<section>\n\t\t\t\t<p>We are proud of the following accreditations, which reflect our standing as a progressive and sustainable fine building company.<\/p>\n\t\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t<h1>The Chartered Institute of Building <\/h1>\n\t\t\t<section>\n\t\t\t\t<p>Hale is a Chartered Building Company. The internationally recognised charter acknowledges our professional development, rigorous processes, ethical practice and unrelenting standards. As part of this exclusive group, we garner support and inspiration from fellow members and can contribute to positive change across the industry.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ciob.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"underline light\">The Chartered Institute of Building<\/a><\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"172\" height=\"71\" src=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/New-CIOB-Chartered-Building-Company-Logo-with-strapline-172x71.jpg\" class=\"attachment-Xx71 size-Xx71\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/New-CIOB-Chartered-Building-Company-Logo-with-strapline-172x71.jpg 172w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/New-CIOB-Chartered-Building-Company-Logo-with-strapline-300x124.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/New-CIOB-Chartered-Building-Company-Logo-with-strapline-1024x422.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/New-CIOB-Chartered-Building-Company-Logo-with-strapline-768x317.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/New-CIOB-Chartered-Building-Company-Logo-with-strapline-1536x634.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/New-CIOB-Chartered-Building-Company-Logo-with-strapline-485x200.jpg 485w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/New-CIOB-Chartered-Building-Company-Logo-with-strapline.jpg 1789w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 172px) 100vw, 172px\" \/><\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t<h1>Federation of Master Builders<\/h1>\n\t\t\t<section>\n\t\t\t\t<p>As a member of the Federation of Master Builders, Hale is recognised as a quality construction company that actively enhances opportunities and champions the best for our industry and customers.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.fmb.org.uk\/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"underline light\">Federation of Master Builders<\/a><\/li>\n\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"118\" height=\"71\" src=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/FMB-logo-horizontal-black-118x71.jpg\" class=\"attachment-Xx71 size-Xx71\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/FMB-logo-horizontal-black-118x71.jpg 118w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/FMB-logo-horizontal-black-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hale.