al-Colour-Alcumus-SafeContractor-200x200.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 71px) 100vw, 71px\" \/><\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t<h1>Carbon Neutral<\/h1>\n\t\t\t<section>\n\t\t\t\t<p>As part of our commitment to achieving the net zero target across construction by 2050, and being a more sustainable builder, we are a carbon neutral company. We advise our clients and choose low-carbon sustainable alternatives where we can and run our business as sustainably as possible.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"123\" height=\"71\" src=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/CFS-CO2-Neutral-Org-002-123x71.png\" class=\"attachment-Xx71 size-Xx71\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/CFS-CO2-Neutral-Org-002-123x71.png 123w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/CFS-CO2-Neutral-Org-002-300x174.png 300w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/CFS-CO2-Neutral-Org-002-346x200.png 346w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/CFS-CO2-Neutral-Org-002.png 517w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 123px) 100vw, 123px\" \/><\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t<h1>Social Responsibility<\/h1>\n\t\t\t<section>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p1\">We recognise the need for everyone to consider their carbon footprint. We have achieved carbon neutral certification with our own offices, and are able to assess the footprint of the projects we work on.<\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">As a business working with high-quality properties,<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0 <\/span>we feel it\u2019s important to remember those less fortunate. This is why we make an annual donation to St Mungo\u2019s homeless charity, to help those without a building to call their home.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"168\" height=\"71\" src=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/In-Aid-of-Colour-168x71.jpg\" class=\"attachment-Xx71 size-Xx71\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/In-Aid-of-Colour-168x71.jpg 168w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/In-Aid-of-Colour-300x127.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/In-Aid-of-Colour.jpg 336w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 168px) 100vw, 168px\" \/><\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t<\/section>\n\t\n\t\t<section class=\"team\" data-colour=\"dark\" data-anchor=\"team\">\n\t\t<header>\n\t\t\t<h1>Our Team<\/h1>\n\t\t<\/header>\n\t\t<div class=\"slides\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"283\" height=\"416\" src=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Christian-Hale-283x416.jpg\" class=\"attachment-283x416 size-283x416\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Christian-Hale-283x416.jpg 283w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Christian-Hale-204x300.jpg 204w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Christian-Hale-48x71.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Christian-Hale.jpg 566w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 283px) 100vw, 283px\" \/><\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t<header>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1>Christian Hale<\/h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Director<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/header>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Christian oversees all of our operations \u2013 checking, questioning and improving so that every detail is set up for success. <\/p>\n<p>At the start of a project, he works closely with architects and designers to fine-tune plans, taking early opportunities to reduce complexity and solve technical challenges. As work progresses he turns his eye to quality control, to guarantee that the highest standards of construction and service are maintained. <\/p>\n<p>Christian is a Chartered Construction Manager and member of The Chartered Institute of Building. Becoming chartered is a fitting tribute to his experience, passion, leadership and commitment to professionalism across all aspects of construction.<\/p>\n<p>Before founding Hale, Christian worked for a boutique residential developer in Knightsbridge and a high-end Chelsea-based designer and contractor. <\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"283\" height=\"416\" src=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Christian-Pond-283x416.jpg\" class=\"attachment-283x416 size-283x416\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Christian-Pond-283x416.jpg 283w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Christian-Pond-204x300.jpg 204w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Christian-Pond-48x71.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Christian-Pond.jpg 566w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 283px) 100vw, 283px\" \/><\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t<header>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1>Christian Pond<\/h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Contract Manager<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/header>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Christian oversees a project from the first briefing through to completion and handover. He manages the construction programme and acts as the primary contact for client, architect and site manager throughout. <\/p>\n<p>Christian lives in the detail of the entire design process: working with architects and designers, interpreting the brief, translating it into design, and anticipating any issues before they arise.<\/p>\n<p>During his 20-year career, Christian has performed a number of construction, design and management roles, and founded and run his own property company. <\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"283\" height=\"416\" src=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/jos-283x416.jpg\" class=\"attachment-283x416 size-283x416\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/jos-283x416.jpg 283w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/jos-204x300.jpg 204w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/jos-48x71.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/jos.jpg 566w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 283px) 100vw, 283px\" \/><\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t<header>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1>Jos Gibson <\/h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Contracts Manager<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/header>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Jos oversees Hale\u2019s projects, working alongside the architect, project team and site team, including sub-contractors and specialists, to manage the entire build process.<\/p>\n<p>Personable and thorough, with proven problem-solving ability, Jos ensures the smooth and successful delivery of each project. <\/p>\n<p>With a degree in Architecture, Jos is able to bring his design and technical skills to the table, as well as his prior experience working for a London-based development management company where he oversaw projects from concept to handover. With 7 years\u2019 experience in the industry, Jos has worked across a range of projects that includes listed buildings, refurbishments and new builds.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"283\" height=\"416\" src=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Bryan-Kirkham-2-283x416.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-283x416 size-283x416\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Bryan-Kirkham-2-283x416.jpeg 283w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Bryan-Kirkham-2-204x300.jpeg 204w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Bryan-Kirkham-2-48x71.jpeg 48w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Bryan-Kirkham-2.jpeg 566w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 283px) 100vw, 283px\" \/><\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t<header>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1>Bryan Kirkham<\/h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Quantity Surveyor<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/header>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Bryan manages the commercial aspects of projects, including tendering, procurement, cash flow forecasting, and commercial reporting.<\/p>\n<p>As a people person he enjoys working as part of a team to bring clients\u2019 dreams to life. Commercially astute, he is able to use his experience, his head for numbers, and his talent for deal-making to achieve the most with any budget. <\/p>\n<p>Bryan has 18 years construction industry experience under his belt, working on both residential and commercial projects: from home extensions to \u00a325m buildings at London\u2019s O2 arena. <\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"283\" height=\"416\" src=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Maxine-Allen-283x416.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-283x416 size-283x416\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Maxine-Allen-283x416.jpeg 283w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Maxine-Allen-204x300.jpeg 204w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Maxine-Allen-48x71.jpeg 48w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Maxine-Allen.jpeg 566w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 283px) 100vw, 283px\" \/><\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t<header>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1>Maxine Allen<\/h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Accounts Manager<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/header>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Maxine oversees our accounts, taking care of all day-to-day financial tasks such as paying sub-contractors, arranging supplies and tracking sales expenses.<\/p>\n<p>Friendly and approachable, she enjoys getting to know the whole team on a project, including clients, suppliers and sub-contractors.<\/p>\n<p>Maxine began her career as an office junior with a family-run glass merchants, before later moving into construction, the industry she now considers home.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"283\" height=\"416\" src=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Claire-J-283x416.jpg\" class=\"attachment-283x416 size-283x416\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Claire-J-283x416.jpg 283w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Claire-J-204x300.jpg 204w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Claire-J-48x71.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Claire-J.jpg 566w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 283px) 100vw, 283px\" \/><\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t<header>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1>Claire Jenkins<\/h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Buyer<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/header>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Claire is responsible for sourcing and purchasing materials for Hale\u2019s portfolio of fine building projects. She collates the right information to be sent to suppliers to enable correct quotations and deliveries, and inputs into Hale\u2019s Information Release Schedules to ensure accuracy of delivery.<\/p>\n<p>Her role demands attention to detail as well as good communication and negotiation skills.<br \/>\nShe enjoys building relationships with suppliers and working collaboratively with the Hale team to provide them with the detailed information they need.<\/p>\n<p>Claire has been within the construction industry for eight years, having previously worked as a Buyer for a dry-lining company that dealt with renovation and new build projects in London. <\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"283\" height=\"416\" src=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Adam-Vimmer-portrait-283x416.jpg\" class=\"attachment-283x416 size-283x416\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Adam-Vimmer-portrait-283x416.jpg 283w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Adam-Vimmer-portrait-204x300.jpg 204w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Adam-Vimmer-portrait-48x71.jpg 48w, https:\/\/hale.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Adam-Vimmer-portrait.jpg 566w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 283px) 100vw, 283px\" \/><\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t<header>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1>Adam Wimmer<\/h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Project Surveyor\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/header>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Adam keeps the budget in check through the entire commercial process, from procurement to completion.<\/p>\n<p>With his personable approach and considerable practical experience, Adam ensures the client\u2019s vision becomes reality, minimising risk and maximising cost-efficiencies while aligning with the quality standards we uphold at Hale.<\/p>\n<p>Adam has a Masters in Building Rehabilitation and has filled PQS and QS roles for a major consultancy company, commercial property developers and London-based contractors for more than 14 years, working on retail, leisure and domestic projects of various sizes. <\/p>\n<p>He is highly motivated, has a keen eye for detail, a particular affinity for intricate schemes and a passion for refurbishment and heritage projects.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":2,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.13 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Hale - The quality of our finished build is born from our attention to detail<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"From pricing, programming, site management, completion and hand over we believe that the quality of the build is our most important form of advertising.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/hale.uk\/about\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta 